snippet.title: Ghosts of Tabor - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase Winter 2023
snippet.description: Watch the latest trailer for Ghosts of Tabor for a peek at gameplay and more from this upcoming VR FPS PVP and PVE survival game. In Ghosts of Tabor, use your wits, skills, and resources to survive. The game features different scenarios from scavenging to looting and crafting. Will you survive long enough to make it out alive? Ghosts of Tabor will be available on the Meta Quest Store in 2024 and it is available now in Early Access on Steam and Meta Quest.
